  "content": "span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    Real trace data from the running system. Every search, every embedding,<br>\n    every store operation. The agent reads these to understand performance.\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"terminal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;\">\n    <div style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;\">GET /api/dashboard/traces</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">corvia.store.get</span>     <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\">424 calls</span>  p50: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">0.65ms</span>  p99: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">1.10ms</span></div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">corvia.store.search</span>  <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\"> 23 calls</span>  p50: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">26ms</span>    p95: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">115ms</span></div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">corvia.rag.context</span>   <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\"> 23 calls</span>  p50: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">42ms</span>    p95: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">135ms</span></div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">corvia.entry.embed</span>   <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\"> 25 calls</span>  p50: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">14ms</span>    p95: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">36ms</span></div>\n    <div><span style=\"color: var(--accent-green);\">corvia.entry.write</span>   <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\">  2 calls</span>  avg: <span style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">88ms</span></div>\n  </div>",
